$interpreted: Izumi: My oh my, you gotta see it to believe it. No truer words were ever spoken...
Izumi: Lemme see, Atlas Marionette Workshop I...
Izumi: This cry for help... Did it come from within the workshop...?
Pero: T, thank goodness that you passed by, or else I would've died. Thank you...
Pero: I'm Pero. I came to Atlas after I heard the rumor. You're here for the same reason too, right?
Pero: Yeah. Rumor says that the castle collapse was the handiwork of a demihuman organization. Right now, that organization is still stationed in Atlas.
Izumi: ... Yep, exactly. I'm also here at Atlas to check that out.
Pero: That's great news to hear! Let's travel together. There really are a lot of monsters here——
Pero: Wh, what are you exactly...!?
Izumi: ... Oopsie daisy, accidentally revealed my true identity.
Izumi: Well, excuse me for what's going to happen next~
Izumi: ... You really do have quite the terrible luck.
